data.description: Brand New Roof was just put on in December of 2023 on this Well-Maintained Property.  Plenty of room for the entire family in this nice, well maintained, 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, boasting over 2200 finished square feet.  Sitting in a great location on just shy of a quarter of an acre lot.  Main level has 3 bedrooms and a bath room, a gas fireplace in the living room, updated windows and a big laundry room with soaking sink.  Lower level of home has 2 bedrooms and a bath room, with a wood fireplace and luxury vinyl plank flooring in the family room.  Tile flooring in bathroom, lots of built-in cabinets in the bedroom and approximately a 10x20 unfinished storage area.  Energy efficient gas heat with central air and water softener.  Covered patio on North side of home.  Lots of room for garden area.  Automatic sprinkler system.  Big Bully Barn in the back yard.  Two-car carport with storage in front of carport.  A new roof was put on in December 2023.  Don’t miss this must-see home!
